## Context Engineering Rules

### Token Budgets

| File Type | Limit |
|-----------|-------|
| CLAUDE.md | < 60 lines |
| Agent files | < 200 lines |
| Skill SKILL.md | < 100 lines |
| Skill detail files | < 500 lines |

### JIT Loading Strategy

1. Load CLAUDE.md on session start
2. Load KOS/ system docs based on task
3. Load skills/ based on command context
4. Never front-load all documentation

